                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Mediocre, careless</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (crimson)</seg>
                        Scribe: Kǝnfa Gabrǝʾel Fǝśśǝḥa. The
                        colophon mentiones ʾabbā Kǝnfa Gabrǝʾel Fǝśśǝḥa as the scribe.<date>Mid-20th
                           century</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the scribe; a few groups of
                           lines (alternating with black lines) in the incipit page; elements of the
                           punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
